tika.dc.description:
You'll love this book, the recipes are easy, the ingredients are easy to get and they don't take long to make. Foodlovers turn to Ranch Dressing Greats for information and inspiration.

Everything is in here, from the proverbial soup to nuts: Best-Ever Stuffed Mushrooms, Smoked Pork Loin, Tijuana Beans, Tomato Sauce With Rose, Vegetable Christmas Tree ...and much much more!

This is a very satisfying book, however I would recommend you eat something before you read this book, or you won't be able to make it through without reaching for a skillet or saucepan!

Ranch Dressing Greats is packed with more information than you could imagine. 44 delicious dishes covering everything, each employing ingredients that should be simple to find and include Ranch Dressing. This cookbook offers great value and would make a fabulous gift.

This book will also give you enough inspiration to experiment with different ingredients since you'll find the extensive index to be extremely...
